casebody.data:
Nicole Rena MCCREA, Petitioner
v.
DISTRICT OF COLUMBIA OFFICE OF HUMAN RIGHTS, et al. No. 19-7389 Supreme Court of the United States. February 24, 2020

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the District of Columbia Court of Appeals dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
